==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Eburnation
<hw>E`bur*na"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>eburnus</ets> of ivory, fr. <ets>ebur</ets> ivory: cf. F.
<ets>⟦eacute⟧burnation</ets>. See <er>Ivory</er>.]</ety>
<fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>A condition of bone cartilage occurring in
certain diseases of these tissues, in which they acquire an unnatural
density, and come to resemble ivory.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Eburnean</ent>⟦br⟧
